      <title>官方媒体称越南立法机关批准主席辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-legislature-approves-resignation-president-state-media-says-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体报道，越南立法机构周四批准了国家主席武文上的辞职，这是在执政的共产党加强反腐打击行动中最新一位辞职的高级官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-legislature-approves-resignation-president-state-media-says-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 04:21:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着移民数量创历史新高，澳大利亚收紧​​学生签证规定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-tightens-student-visa-rules-migration-hits-record-high-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚将于本周开始对外国学生实施更严格的签证规定，因为官方数据显示移民人数再创新高，这可能会进一步加剧本已紧张的租赁市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-tightens-student-visa-rules-migration-hits-record-high-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师称，印度尼西亚总统候选人阿尼斯呼吁重新举行选举</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-presidential-candidate-anies-calls-election-re-run-lawyer-says-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚落败的总统候选人阿尼斯·巴斯韦丹 (Anies Baswedan) 的律师阿里·优素福·阿米尔 (Ari Yusuf Amir) 周四表示，他已要求宪法法院下令重新举行选举，将佐科·维多多总统的儿子排除在外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-presidential-candidate-anies-calls-election-re-run-lawyer-says-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:57:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国驻澳大利亚大使表示正在配合腐败调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-ambassador-australia-says-hes-cooperating-with-graft-probe-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国驻澳大利亚大使周四表示，他愿意接受反腐败机构的质询，因为有指控称他去年担任国防部长期间试图操纵对一名海军陆战队员死亡事件的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-ambassador-australia-says-hes-cooperating-with-graft-probe-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:52:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国王毅与澳大利亚前总理基廷进行“大局”会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-wang-yi-has-big-picture-talks-with-former-australia-pm-keating-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京表示，中国外交部长王毅周四会见了澳大利亚前总理保罗·基廷，并强调北京希望美国盟友澳大利亚奉行独立的外交政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-wang-yi-has-big-picture-talks-with-former-australia-pm-keating-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:39:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港央行维持关键利率不变，追踪美联储举措</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracking-fed-move-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港金融管理局 (HKMA) 周四将通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率维持在 5.75% 不变，以追随美联储维持利率稳定的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracking-fed-move-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称新西兰个人银行服务竞争有限</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/limited-competition-personal-banking-services-new-zealand-report-says-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰竞争监管机构周四表示，由于价格匹配策略以及缺乏推动变革的颠覆性力量，新西兰四大银行在个人银行服务方面的竞争有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/limited-competition-personal-banking-services-new-zealand-report-says-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:25:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚总统候选人阿尼斯向法庭质疑选举结果</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-presidential-candidate-anies-files-court-challenge-election-result-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[落败的印度尼西亚总统候选人阿尼斯·巴斯韦丹周四向宪法法院提起法律诉讼，质疑国防部长普拉博沃·苏比安托以压倒性优势获胜的选举结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-presidential-candidate-anies-files-court-challenge-election-result-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 03:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾以安全风险为由建议总统不要访问南海</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/citing-safety-risk-taiwan-recommends-president-does-not-visit-schina-sea-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾最高安全官员周四表示，鉴于中国在南海的军事存在，他目前不建议蔡英文总统访问南海，因为她的飞行可能面临“相关国家干涉”的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/citing-safety-risk-taiwan-recommends-president-does-not-visit-schina-sea-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:33:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰间谍机构审查建议对其托管的任何外国合作伙伴能力进行审计</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-spy-agency-review-suggests-audit-any-foreign-partner-capabilities-it-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对新西兰一家间谍机构的审查表明，在对其托管外国信号情报系统进行调查后，该机构需要对其可能为其他国家运营的任何能力进行审核。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-spy-agency-review-suggests-audit-any-foreign-partner-capabilities-it-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:26:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
